Exercise 1.8: ExecutorService Orchestration
→ Refactor order matching to use a FixedThreadPool of size Runtime.getRuntime().availableProcessors().
→ Use Future<MatchResult> to retrieve results and handle ExecutionException gracefully.
→ Print throughput: orders matched per second averaged over 5 runs.

